long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
LogBaker is an extra toolkit for Piwik PRO Analytics Suite.

Explore:
Display sidebar alongside your website and automatically see statistics for each page your browsing
Enable an interactive overlay based on heatmaps data to see what users are exactly clicking!

Download:
Easily define queries for fetching your Piwik PRO Sessions, Events and Query data.
You can create multiple queries to multiple instances.
Big amounts of data are fetched in chunks.
